{"tid":1255783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢嘅各位洗唔洗檢討一下以後行動嘅集合時間？","createTime":"2019-06-24T16:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T16:03:26.000Z","uid":89185,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"710258204992428b002eb8d615fb5b4b0b84d0d3","tid":1255783,"uid":89185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:00:15.000Z","msg":"好似今日咁，早上集合始終會比較少人能夠出黎，似乎大家嘅病假事假都有限，三罷成效亦較低。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行動人數較以往低，我偏向相信係因為較多人抽唔到身早上去，而唔係因為開始灰心。<br />\n所以我認為大家需要檢討一下唔同行動嘅集合時間。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係遊擊，動員人數可以較少，又或者星期六日行動，咁集合時間早啲都唔怕。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果係大行動，咁可能將集合時間定返晏啲會比較好，遷就返大家下班時間。我絕對相信極大量發夢嘅兄弟放工後會仆出黎增援。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位兄弟不妨講吓自己意見，一齊諗方法做得更好。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">互相支持，互相鼓勵，互相配合！</span>"},{"pid":"e409adfb62cb8afc4d666cf7f880d221f8fcf328","tid":1255783,"uid":89185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:01:10.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"44e637f73c8bbf5b9db7009d4491179463d7e7fd","tid":1255783,"uid":89185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:02:28.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"1c233455485858acfea26442fab6961cb2c19df9","tid":1255783,"uid":89185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:03:26.000Z","msg":"推！"}]}